This is a sample project that makes use of the following open source projects

Buildout - Dependency Management - http://www.buildout.org/
Django - Web Framework - http://www.djangoproject.com
Celery - Asynchronous Task Queue - http://ask.github.com/celery/


The sample Blog application has a sample Celery task defined that will print a message every minute.

To start the task queue run the following command:

bin/manage.py celeryd -v 2 -B -s celery -E -l INFO